%% Data Flow Diagram: llama-stack-provider-ragas
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as RagasEvaluatorInline
    participant DSIO as DatasetIO API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Inf as Inference API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Ollama as Ollama/vLLM<br/>11434/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,Ollama: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation

    Client->>LS: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS->>Inline: dispatch eval request
    Inline->>DSIO: fetch dataset (in-process)
    DSIO-->>Inline: dataset rows
    Inline->>Inf: LLM completions (in-process)
    Inf->>Ollama: HTTP 11434/TCP<br/>plaintext, no auth
    Ollama-->>Inf: completion response
    Inline->>Inf: embeddings (in-process)
    Inf->>Ollama: HTTP 11434/TCP<br/>plaintext, no auth
    Ollama-->>Inf: embedding vectors
    Inline-->>LS: evaluation results
    Client->>LS: GET /alpha/eval/job-result<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS-->>Client: Ragas metrics (answer_relevancy,<br/>context_precision, faithfulness,<br/>context_recall)

    participant Remote as RagasEvaluatorRemote
    participant KFP as KFP API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KPod as KFP Pipeline Pod
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)

    Client->>LS: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS->>Remote: dispatch eval request
    Remote->>KFP: POST healthz check<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Remote: healthy
    Remote->>KFP: POST create_run<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Remote: run_id
    Remote-->>LS: job submitted (async)
    LS-->>Client: job_id

    Note over KPod: Pipeline executes asynchronously
    KPod->>LS: GET dataset<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS-->>KPod: dataset rows
    KPod->>LS: POST completions<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS-->>KPod: LLM responses
    KPod->>LS: POST embeddings<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS-->>KPod: embedding vectors
    KPod->>S3: PUT results<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, AWS IAM

    Client->>LS: GET /alpha/eval/job-status<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS->>Remote: check status
    Remote->>KFP: GET run status<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Remote: SUCCEEDED
    Remote->>S3: GET results<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, AWS IAM
    S3-->>Remote: evaluation results
    Remote-->>LS: results
    LS-->>Client: Ragas metrics
